Description: Yan 2023 homotopic brain parcellation for the 'ggseg' ecosystem.
    Provides 'ggseg_atlas' objects with 2D polygon geometry and 3D vertex
    indices. Includes 7-network and 17-network variants at resolutions
    from 100 to 1000 parcels.
